# Outcast - iOS Podcast Player App

## Project Overview
This is a SwiftUI-based podcast player app for iOS.

## Tech Stack
- Swift 5
- SwiftUI
- Xcode project (not SPM-based)
- Target: iOS

## Code Style
- Use SwiftUI for all new views
- Follow Apple's Swift API Design Guidelines
- Use `@State`, `@Binding`, `@ObservableObject` appropriately
- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Use meaningful variable and function names

## File Organization
- Views go in the main Outcast/ folder
- Models should be separate from views
- Keep files focused and single-purpose

## Reference
- Pocket Casts iOS app is available at ../references/pocket-casts-ios for architecture reference

